    "To counter this, we have assembled 30 new datasets, as described in Section 3.1.",
    "Figure 41 shows the ranks for the eight best of category on these data sets.",
    "The top clique for accuracy contains MR-Hydra, HC2, RDST, QUANT and FreshPRINCE.",
    "The results for balanced accuracy are similar.",
    "Figure 42 shows the results for the combined 142 datasets."
